GitLab Main Features
│
├── Version Control
│   ├── Git repository management
│   ├── Branching and merging
│   ├── Merge requests (PR equivalent)
│   └── Code review & approval workflows
│
├── CI/CD (Continuous Integration / Continuous Delivery)
│   ├── Pipelines for automated builds, tests, and deployments
│   ├── Auto DevOps (predefined CI/CD templates)
│   ├── Multi-stage pipelines
│   ├── Manual and scheduled jobs
│   └── Environment management & deployments
│
├── Project Management
│   ├── Issue tracking
│   ├── Milestones & roadmaps
│   ├── Epics & task boards
│   └── Burndown charts & analytics
│
├── Security & Compliance
│   ├── Static Application Security Testing (SAST)
│   ├── Dynamic Application Security Testing (DAST)
│   ├── Dependency Scanning
│   ├── Container Scanning
│   ├── License compliance checks
│   └── Audit logs & access control
│
├── Code Quality & Testing
│   ├── Unit & integration testing in pipelines
│   ├── Code coverage reports
│   ├── Linting & formatting
│   └── Merge request approvals & code review rules
│
├── Package & Container Registry
│   ├── Built-in Docker registry
│   ├── Support for Maven, NPM, PyPI, Helm charts
│   └── Artifact storage for CI/CD jobs
│
├── Monitoring & Observability
│   ├── Prometheus integration
│   ├── Metrics dashboards
│   ├── Alerts and notifications
│   └── Error tracking
│
├── Collaboration & Communication
│   ├── Wiki & documentation
│   ├── Discussion threads on issues & merge requests
│   ├── Notifications & mentions
│   └── Code snippets / snippets sharing
│
├── DevSecOps Automation
│   ├── Security scans in pipelines
│   ├── Compliance automation
│   └── Policy enforcement
│
└── Integrations & Extensibility
    ├── Webhooks & APIs
    ├── Third-party integrations (Slack, Jira, Kubernetes)
    ├── GitLab Runner for custom CI/CD execution
    └── GitOps support with Kubernetes
